name: Swarovski Crystal Purple Heart Earrings (Heliotrope OR Bermuda Blue)
description:
THE DETAILS

These hearts are gorgeous in person. Swarovski crystal in a rich royal purple with blue tones and lots of sparkle. Swarovski calls this color Heliotrope.  Also available in Swarovski Crystal Bermuda Blue. For Bermuda Blue, simple select your color upon check out.

10mm heliotrope Swarovski Crystal hearts, silver plated small kidney style earring hooks, measures slightly less than 1" from top of hook to bottom of heart point

name: Scissor Charm Glass Diamond Necklace
description:
THE DETAILS

This super cute and elegant necklace would make a perfect gift for your pet groomer, hairstylist or even your wedding seamstress! The clear rhinestone shines and flashes like a diamond.

2.5" tall x 1" wide (at the widest part which is the handles) metal charm, silver plated bow charm and sparkling glass rhinestone set in a silver plated setting. 

The chain is a textured silver plated chain with lobster claw clasp for easy adornment.  You may select from several different length chain options.

name: Swarvoski Crystal Heart Bow Earrings (Bermuda Blue or Heliotrope)
description:
THE DETAILS

10x20 mm antiqued silver bow charms with 10mm Swarvoski crystals hearts in Bermuda Blue, new white gold plated lever back earring, each earring is approximately 1.25" from top of hook to bottom of hearts.

Also available in Swarovski color Heliotrope (purple).

name: Diamond Rhinestone Glass Earrings
description:
THE DETAILS

8mm, 6mm and 4mm glass clear jewels are nestled one on top of the other in this gorgeous pair of long dangle earrings. These would be perfect for a wedding. They have a modern twist with a vintage look. The setting is silver plated. Earring hooks are 100% brand new silver plated lever back style. Each earring measure 1.5" from top of the hook to bottom of the last jewel.
